BBNaija Season 7 housemate Etsanyi ‘Beauty’ Tukura has said she does not mind staying single for life. The 24-year-old model and lawyer from Taraba State disclosed this in chit-chat with fellow housemates.   Tonto Dikeh laments losing over 800 poultry chicks     I’ve an albino twin brother – Daniella     Ladies overwhelm Eloswag with twerking   “I don’t mind staying single for life because I’m particular about being with the right person when it comes to marriage,” she said. Beauty was crowned Miss Nigeria in 2019, becoming the 43rd beauty to win the crown. She was also crowned ‘Most Beautiful Girl in Taraba’ from 2015 to 2017.